messages.message:
hey folks, we should _never_ be using origin header to bypass csrf. `Origin: INSTABASE_ORIGIN` header was meant for a special case: jupyter notebook needing to communicate with Instabase platform. With notebook being deprecated, we should remove this special case.

Also, any API request should live only in api-server and should be called using an OAuth Token.

@shaunak let's work together on deprecating this header
